(- Bottom Line) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The current Atho packaging flow favors reproducibility and operational reliability over) Tj
T*
(installer-style polish. That tradeoff is intentional for alpha hardening. Until path migration) Tj
T*
(and freeze tooling are fully mature, this repository-preserving packaging strategy remains the) Tj
T*
(safest way to distribute consistent runtime artifacts.) Tj
T*
